window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>There are moments in life when magic happens. They occur when we feel something \"click\" inside us, like turning on the light in a dark room. It happens in an instant, but suddenly we know that nothing will ever be the same. We feel that \"click\" when a new idea or vision strikes us that will change our life, and perhaps the lives of others as well. How do these \"clicks\" that open new horizons occur? Are there ways to provoke them or, at least, to encourage them?</p> <p>Francesc Miralles, a global authority on new trends and co-author of <i>Ikigai</i>, translated into seventy languages, explains in this revealing audiobook how these portals to radical change and success work.</p>"; 
